# ScholarLens: Fine-tuning Qwen1.5-1.8B for Essay Evaluation

A QLoRA-tuned model for structured scholarship essay feedback (Strengths / Weaknesses / Scores / Summary).  
Trained on ~1K curated examples with near-100% JSON validity and released on HuggingFace Hub as `NewJetsada/ScholarLens`.

## Installation
```bash
pip install -q transformers==4.44.0 trl==0.23.0 peft accelerate bitsandbytes

Open the notebook Qwen_1_8B.ipynb in Google Colab, run cells step-by-step, and edit the essay variable to test feedback generation.


